  "narrative": "# Turn 1\n\n*8 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 1 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W10.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W25, W19.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships.\n\n### OMEGA (berserker)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W8, W10.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W28, W28.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W17, W9.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W15, W13.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W16, W2.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships; invested in 2 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W3, W4.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; commissioned 25 new ships.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **OMEGA** seized control of W8 (previously TERRAN).\n\n- **PROPHET** seized control of W28 (previously neutral territory).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F7\u2192W10\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F15\u2192W25, F16\u2192W19\n\n- **OMEGA** moved: F9\u2192W8, F10\u2192W10\n\n- **PROPHET** moved: F11\u2192W28, F12\u2192W28\n\n- **REAVER** moved: F5\u2192W17, F6\u2192W9\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F1\u2192W15, F2\u2192W13\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F14\u2192W16, F13\u2192W2\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F4\u2192W3, F3\u2192W4\n\n### Production\n\n- **CURATOR** launched 18 new ships.\n\n- **NOMAD** launched 18 new ships.\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 19 new ships.\n\n- **REAVER** launched 22 new ships.\n\n- **TERRAN** launched 6 new ships.\n\n- **TRADER** launched 14 new ships.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 2 industry.\n"
